FBIS3-37705 "drsov035_a_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Yeltsin Stresses Need for Political Settlement in Bosnia LD1802170594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1557 GMT 18 Feb 94 LD1802170594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Moscow, 18 Feb -- "In the last few days Russian Federation President Boris Yeltsin has been exchanging messages with leaders of the states most actively participating in the search for a solution to the Bosnian problem," says an official statement issued by the presidential press service today. "In these messages the countries involved have expressed their positions with regard to this problem. The Russian president stated his views on the situation that had developed, stressing the need for political settlement and stopping the bloodshed in Bosnia," the press service reports.
